    "From the model interpretation analysis, we study two cases on hypertension and heart failure prediction.",
    "The top 20 important features we get corresponds to the medical knowledge with the domain expert.",
    "So our model can produce precise as well as interpretable predictions on the health events.",
    "From the collaboration with domain expert in the cardiology diseases, we can validate some already known medical knowledge and discover some new features which lacks enough attention previously.",
    "The CKLE can not only precisely predict health events but also can discover some medical findings."
